'''Alityum''' ( s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tinglizt]] : Lithium, ikkad [[tagrigit]] : lithos, lli igan [[aẓru]]), iga yan [[Afrḍis akimyan|ufrḍis akimi]] lli ila tasdugmt n '''Li''' d uṭṭun afrḍas 3. Iga yan ''alkali metal'' ilgʷaɣn d [[Aklu|akʷlu]] nns iga anqʷri-umlil. Ɣ kra n izmaz ar ittga tidi ''(metal)'' lli kullu fssusn ɣ umaḍal. 

Ur ar ittili ɣ tamust ''(nature)'' waḥdut, mac ɣ tguditin, zun d ''pegmatite'', lli akkʷ igan aɣbalu n alityum. S tzgi nns ɣ waddad n ayun, ar ittigut ufrḍis ad waman n [[ill]] d [[Aman|waman]] n [[Tis|tisnt]] s uzgzl.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lithium</ref>

== Tawuri ==
